headline: Add These 4 GARP Stocks to Your Portfolio to Receive Handsome Returns
summary: The GARP strategy helps investors gain exposure to stocks that have solid prospects and are trading at a discount. VRT, EXPE, NVDA and AMP are some such stocks.
